%% Diagram: W3C Trace Context propagation across three services
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Gateway as Edge / Gateway
    participant Orders as Orders service
    participant Payments as Payments service

    Note over Gateway: Mint root span\ntraceparent 00-{trace}-{spanA}-01
    Gateway->>Orders: HTTP + traceparent + tracestate
    Note over Orders: Extract context, start spanB\nparent = spanA
    Orders->>Payments: HTTP + traceparent (spanB) + baggage
    Note over Payments: Child spanC\nread baggage user.tier=premium
    Payments-->>Orders: 200 OK
    Orders-->>Gateway: 200 OK
    Note over Gateway,Payments: Each service async-exports its span via OTLP.\nBackend reassembles the DAG by trace-id.
